name: Confusing Mess #4
description: Why should we be apathetic with technology and all its accelaration? it seems that the world will be more "chaotic" if humanity continuously show no interest towards it. "It feels right to describe our current situation with the term “chaotic”, as everyone is expected to be able to do anything in the internet world. Meanwhile, many are ignorant about technology. They feel that technology is a contradiction against human behavior, whereas actually, human beings are just confusing themselves by ignoring technology.
